dc_description_s: This data layer represents parcels for Portage County, Wisconsin in 2015. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Portage_Parcels_2015.gdb. [The Parcel data set is a vector representation of tax parcel boundaries and associated parcel attributes in Portage County, Wisconsin. The parcels are created by using coordinate geometry and digitizing from digital orthophotography.
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements.
